## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of recent data and the potential bias in opinion pieces. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of the space industry means that new developments could quickly alter the landscape. The report relies on sources up to October 2023, and any developments beyond this date are not considered. Furthermore, the perspectives included may not fully represent the diversity of opinions on this topic.